review:
I was very particular while booking the appointment itself that only Dr. Yashwanth should do the treatments I require. However I was just given consultation by him and a list of procedures to do with costs and one particular procedure for Rs. 20,000/- when all I went was for a check up. 

And subsequently a junior doctor was asked to do the procedure.

After which I was in severe pain and full mouth was paining. Today when I called I was told Dr. Anjali who has so many yrs experience, will see me and she too spoke to me asking me to come. But when I went, she made me sit and called Dr. Yashwanth. 

After that a mouth wash was to be given to me. When the clinic boy was told to get it, there was so much drama happening. I was told to pay him for it before he even got the mouth wash and everyone were just so unprofessional.

It was a very scary experience.

The team comprising of Dr Pandian, Sr Dendist Mrs Anjali,and other staff members working under his guidance are highly experienced, dedicated and committed to their assigned duty.They provided me the world class dental treatment and I enjoyed it all along. 

Smile is a very valuable trait of  human being and now I can smile as pleasingly as ever

My best wishes for your bright future

Smilingly 
R.Ganesan
